title: Head of Immigration apologises for 'regrettable' Border Force press release
text: The secretary of the Immigration Department apologised today for what he called a regrettable incident over a media release sent out by the Border Force Agency which sparked protests in Melbourne. Mike Pezzullo faced detailed questioning in the Senate about "Operation Fortitude", which was to have happened over a weekend in Melbourne in August. ...
